{/* Rosie never miss a call Section */}

Rosie makes sure you
never miss a call.

✓
Trained on your business and reviewed by you, Rosie always provides accurate info to callers.
✓
Available 24/7/365 — taking calls and answering questions anytime you can’t.
✓
Only $49/month gets you a custom greeting, spam filtering, FAQs, and instant notifications of every call.
{/* Three Bad Options Section */}

Currently, you have three bad
options for tackling incoming calls:

✕
Answer every call
yourself
  • ✕ Constant interruptions during the day
  • ✕ Wasted time on spam calls
  • ✕ Always chasing people down
✕
Send calls you can’t answer to
voicemail
  • ✕ Most people don’t leave a message
  • ✕ Hard to find time to call back
  • ✕ Impossible to reach them again
✕
Pay too much for an outsourced
service
  • ✕ Every call costs $2/minute
  • ✕ Long hold times for callers
  • ✕ Inconsistent service from untrained receptionists

{/* Hero Section */}
NEW Unlimited minutes on all plans

AI answering service for your business calls

Rosie is your AI answering service — trained on your business and ready to field calls, answer questions, set appointments, and send you all the details 24/7.

Start Free Trial
{/* Placeholder for chat mockup image */}
{/* Three Bad Options Section */}

Currently, you have three bad
options for tackling incoming calls:

✕
Answer every call
yourself
  • ✕ Constant interruptions during the day
  • ✕ Wasted time on spam calls

service
  • ✕ Every call costs $2/minute
  • ✕ Long hold times for callers

{/* Features Grid Section */}

Rosie adapts to your business,
whether service-based or brick and mortar.

{/* SVG user check */}
Service existing customers
Rosie answers questions about booking, hours, billing, and more.
{/* SVG phone */}
Handle incoming leads
Rosie gives prospects the answers they need, books appointments, and keeps you in the loop.
{/* SVG bell */}
Minimize in-store disruptions
Rosie answers FAQs and transfers calls to employees on the floor only when necessary.
{/* SVG filter */}
Filter out sales calls & spam
Rosie screens and blocks 1-800s, robocalls, and sales reps, only spending time on important calls.
{/* Features Section */}

Why Rosie?

24/7 AI Chat Support

Never miss a customer. Rosie answers instantly, any time.

Easy Integration

Embed Rosie on your website in minutes, no code required.

Customizable Workflows

Tailor Rosie to your business needs and automate tasks.

{/* Testimonials Section */}

What Our Customers Say

"Rosie has transformed our customer support!"

- Jane, SaaS Founder

"Easy to set up and our clients love it."

- Mike, Agency Owner
{/* Pricing Section */}

Pricing

Starter

$29/mo

  • Basic AI Chatbot
  • Email Support
  • 1 Website
Get Started

Pro

$59/mo

  • Advanced AI Chatbot
  • Priority Support
  • Unlimited Websites
Get Started
{/* FAQ Section */}

Frequently Asked Questions

How do I install Rosie?

Just copy-paste a code snippet into your website or use our integrations.

Can I customize Rosie?

Yes! You can change responses, workflows, and appearance.

Is there a free trial?

Yes, try Rosie free for 7 days. No credit card required.

{/* Footer Section */}
